item.description:
Are you HSP, Take the test below. 12 or more trues and you are probably a Highly Sensitive Person:
I seem to be more aware of subtleties in my environment than the
average person True False
I am very sensitive to other people's moods and they can
affect me True False
I can be very intuitive True False
being alone, going for a walk or being in a darkened room
can restore and rejuvenate me True Fase
I have known who was calling on the phone before I picked
it up, what song was playing next before I heard it. True False
I tend to be very sensitive to pain True False
I am very sensitive to the effects of caffeine True False
I have a rich, complex inner life True False
I am made uncomfortable by loud noises True False
I can be overstimulated by new people or people I like
and they or I have misinterpeted that I am interested in them True False
I am deeply moved by the arts or music True False
I can startle easily True False
I am conscientious True False
I can get rattled when I have a lot to do in a short amount of time True False
When people are unconfortable in an environment I tend to know
what needs to be done to make it comfortable(like changing
the lighting, seating or tempature True False
I can get annoyed when people try to get me to do too many
things at once True False
I try hard to avoid making mistakes or forgetting things True False
I make it a point to avoid violent movies and TV shows True False
I become unpleasantly aroused when a lot is going on True False
Being very hungry creates a strong reaction in me True False
Changes in my live can shake me up True False
I notice and enjoy delicate or fine scents, tasts, sounds, works of art True False
When I was a child, my parents or teachers seemed to see me as
senstive or shy True False
When I must compete or be observed while performing a task
I become so nervous or shaky that I do much worse than I would
otherwise True False
I make it a high priority to arrange my life to avoid upsetting or
overwhelming situations True False
I have noticed that sometimes while near or under a streetlight at night
it has suddenly gone off, or if already off it has turned on True False
I sometimes find myself, or enjoy, flipping through a newspaper,
magazine from the Back to the front True False
